    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/2db484421c55b4e12c9c3643fca0072b.poster.avif?t=1730368745\" width=600 height=217 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/2db484421c55b4e12c9c3643fca0072b.webm?t=1730368745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>心事重重的少女入住一所空荡无人的公寓，得到了一本能对话“另一个世界”的笔记本，一场时空交错的历险由此展开。两位身陷囹圄的主人公分别位于时间线的两端，共同收集线索、推理疑案、寻找真相，为无人问津的往事拂去尘埃，踏上寻找真相和彼此救赎之路……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/b99161f727e8790e4ce151a030eb0c65.avif?t=1730368745\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>《交界线》是一款含有灵异要素的剧情向解谜游戏，玩家将操控不同时空中的两位主角，通过和公寓内个性各异的住客们互动交谈、调查房间内的物品、解开谜题获得回忆、推理还原事件真相等方式，再现凝缩在公寓中的人间百态，清扫角色们的遗憾与执念，帮助他们开启下一段旅程。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/33294ab50d8d6d1530aedf0c7e4ec9a2.avif?t=1730368745\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>双主人公处在不同时空开展双线叙事，多重视角纵览剧情因果<br></li><li>剧情以单元剧模式展开，每扇房门后都埋藏着一个家庭的悲剧<br></li><li>搜证谈话解谜流程完备，沉浸式体验抽丝剥茧的推理乐趣<br></li><li>游戏内含多张精美CG，像素风也不乏丰富视觉演出呈现<br></li><li>音效与配乐选取精心打磨，于细节处提升恐怖氛围感</li></ul><br><br>※调查<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/efc26c51617aa98b6bdaaddffe6b7d88.poster.avif?t=1730368745\" width=580 height=323 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/efc26c51617aa98b6bdaaddffe6b7d88.webm?t=1730368745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>    <br>※互动<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/022db5c75d6bb7d2dec6ecf19f2ffb06.poster.avif?t=1730368745\" width=580 height=323 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/022db5c75d6bb7d2dec6ecf19f2ffb06.webm?t=1730368745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>    <br>※推理<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/f6594477a3b895a613b62dec727faf6d.poster.avif?t=1730368745\" width=580 height=323 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/f6594477a3b895a613b62dec727faf6d.webm?t=1730368745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/3e12d7bc4c383f9bdb8a0f6614abf306.avif?t=1730368745\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>官方QQ群：690881286<br>微博：@indienova<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143050/extras/72ccce79935d4c4855d62937ea245128.avif?t=1730368745\" width=580 height=328 /></span>",
